plot: In "Boys in the Band", Vicky has kidnapped teen singing sensation Chip Skylark, and a stadium full of screaming girls (and Mrs. Turner) is going to tear the town apart if he doesn't perform for them.

How will Timmy prevent the concert, which distracted Timmy's parents from his birthday? Later, when he sees that Chip does not want to disappoint fans, he wants to fix the situation but even magic does not work. what can Timmy do? how will he enjoy both birthdays?+how will Timmy get the privilege for himself and his friends to use the skateboard park?—N the Fan
